[30;1m118 | [0m[35m### Quick migration guide from v1 to v2[0m
[30;1m119 | [0m[35m- Enhancement[0m
[30;1m120 | [0m[35m    - Updated base Selenium Python binding version to v4[0m
[30;1m121 | [0m[35m        - Removed `forceMjsonwp` since Selenium v4 and Appium Python client v2 expect only W3C WebDr[0m
[30;1m122 | [0m[35m    - Methods `ActionHelpers#scroll`, `ActionHelpers#drag_and_drop`, `ActionHelpers#tap`, `ActionHel[0m
[30;1m123 | [0m[35m        - Please check each behavior. Their behaviors could slightly differ.[0m
[30;1m124 | [0m[35m    - Added `strict_ssl` to relax SSL errors such as self-signed ones[0m

[30;1m150 | [0m[35m    - Updated base Selenium Python binding version to v4[0m
[30;1m151 | [0m[35m        - Removed `forceMjsonwp` since Selenium v4 and Appium Python client v2 expect only W3C WebDr[0m
[30;1m152 | [0m[35m    - Methods `ActionHelpers#scroll`, `ActionHelpers#drag_and_drop`, `ActionHelpers#tap`, `ActionHel[0m
[30;1m153 | [0m[35m        - Please check each behavior. Their behaviors could slightly differ.[0m
[30;1m154 | [0m[35m    - Added `strict_ssl` to relax SSL errors such as self-signed ones[0m
